title: Sept 1: Sunny 1bd, 1 bath upper duplex
posting_body: ['Unit 2 is a 1br / 1 bath, upper-level duplex one block west of Como Park.', 'An upper-level duplex with 1 bedroom is a rare find, especially so close to Como Park!', 'The unit is available September 1 for a 1-year term.', 'Current tenants are in the process of moving, so please note current pictures are interspersed with previous pictures to give you a better sense of the unit.', 'Amenities include:', 'High ceilings', 'Dishwasher', 'French doors', 'One off-street parking space included', 'Ceramic tile floors in kitchen and bathroom', 'Free laundry in building', 'Gas range', 'Kitchen pantry', 'Back deck', 'Outdoor Clothesline', 'Significant storage space', 'Central Twin Cities location that is transit & bike friendly.', 'Blocks from: Como Park (including Pool, Zoo & Conservatory), Hamline University, University of Minnesota, Metropolitan State University, and the Minnesota State Fair', 'Transit Friendly', 'Bus Service within walking distance:', 'Route 3A / 3B', '(east-west service to both downtowns)', 'Bus Rapid Transit (BRT)', 'A Line', '(north-south express service, connects to light rail)', 'Route 84', '(north-south local service, connects to light rail)', 'Route 83', '(north-south local service, connects to light rail)', 'Bikeable', 'Como Avenue\'s bike lanes and the neighborhood\'s relatively flat terrain earns a "very bikeable" score of 86 at <URL>.', "The neighborhood's Central location makes biking to either downtown possible:", '4.2 miles to downtown Saint Paul', '5.5 miles to downtown Minneapolis', 'This building is pet friendly; however, some breed restrictions and pet fees will apply.', 'The building is non-smoking, so please keep any smoking outside.', 'Utilities: Owner pays water, sewer, cooking gas and takes care of lawn care and snow removal.', 'Tenant is responsible for electricity.', 'Heat is electric baseboard, so part of the electric bill.', 'There is a fee of $45 to cover the trash each month.', 'Please e-mail with the following information to arrange a showing:', 'Name:', 'Phone:', '# of People & # of Pets:', 'Intended Occupancy Date:', 'Smoking:', 'Landlord Reference Y or N?', 'Thank you!']
